value.title: Will Trump win again? Watch Florida's Sumter County for first election night clue.
value.excerpt: Will Trump win again? Watch Florida's Sumter County for first election night clue. Last week, Democrats took delight in the spectacle of a 500-golf cart flotilla of Joe Biden supporters parading through Florida's largest retirement community en route to turn in their vote-by-mail ballots.

value.title: Trump tweet gave Taliban upper hand in negotiations: Afghan peace official tells Financial Times

value.title: Feds chased suspected foreign link to Trump's 2016 campaign cash for three years
